Inés Faddi Id Guedouz (Arabic, amụrụ n'abalị atọ n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 2001) bụ onye Morocco a mụrụ na Spain nke na agba bọọlụ dị ka onye na agba ọsọ n'etiti maka Primera Federación club Granada CF na otu ụmụ nwanyị nke Morocco.
Faddi agbaala El Olivar, Zaragoza CFF B, Oliver na AEM na Spain.
Faddi mere nnukwu mpụta mbụ ya maka Morocco na 14 June 2021 dị ka nnọchi nkeji nkeji iri asatọ na mmeri n'ụlọ enyi 3-2 meriri Mali..
